  "instructions": [
    "Combine wheat flour and yeast in a large mixing bowl.",
    "Gradually add water and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes until it becomes smooth.",
    "Place the dough in a greased bowl, cover it with a damp cloth, and let it rest in a warm place for 1 hour, or until it has doubled in size.",
    "Steam the dough over boiling water for 10 minutes, or until it's cooked through.",
    "Transfer the dough to a plate and brush with coconut milk.",
    "Add kaffir lime leaves, fish sauce, palm sugar, and chili flakes on top of the dough.",
    "Garnish with toasted peanuts and serve with ice cubes on the side."
  ],
